title: Recruits react to Alabama's 41-23 win over Texas A&M
text:
Several recruits watched Alabama's 41-23 win over Texas A&M and shared their thoughts on social media.
Here are some highlights. This post will be updated.
**Central-Phenix city 2018 elite WR Justyn Ross
Alabama defense is solid right now . 💪🏽
— J-Ross ✈️ (@kvng_ross) October 17, 2015 **Arlington, Texas OL Chris Owens, an Alabama commit
Cam Robinson is eating Myles Garrett up right now 😈🍴
— SwiftCat (@ChrisOwens00) October 17, 2015 And there goes Myles 👀
— SwiftCat (@ChrisOwens00) October 17, 2015 And that's all she wrote🐘🔴 #RollTide
— SwiftCat (@ChrisOwens00) October 17, 2015 **Dadeville athlete Shawn Jennings, committed to Alabama as a defensive back
And another one , pick 6 Eddie Jackson .. Feels good to be committed to the best defense in the country 😎🅰🐘
